/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: SYS_PARAMETER */
/*==============================================================*/
create table SYS_PARAMETER
(
"ParaID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CateName" VARCHAR2(200) not null,
"KeyName" VARCHAR2(200) not null,
"Value" NVARCHAR2(200) not null,
"Comments" NVARCHAR2(500),
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
constraint PK_SYS_PARAMETER primary key ("ParaID")
);

comment on table SYS_PARAMETER is
'系统参数';

comment on column SYS_PARAMETER."Enable" is
'1: 启用
0: 停用';
